{"word":"Shekel","slug":"shekel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shekel</b> A weight equal to twenty gerahs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=13'>Exo 30:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=47'>Num 3:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=12'>Eze 45:12</a><br/> Fractions of, used in currency<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=13'>Exo 30:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=8'>1Sa 9:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=32'>Neh 10:32</a><br/> Used to weigh:<br/> - Gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=22'>Gen 24:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=14'>Num 7:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=86'>Num 7:86</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=21'>Jos 7:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=16'>1Ki 10:16</a> <br/> - Silver<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=21'>Jos 7:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=26'>Jdg 8:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=3'>Jdg 17:3</a> <br/> - Cinnamon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=23'>Exo 30:23</a> <br/> - Hair<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=26'>2Sa 14:26</a> <br/> - Iron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=7'>1Sa 17:7</a> <br/> - Myrrh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=23'>Exo 30:23</a> <br/> - Rations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4&verse=10'>Eze 4:10</a> <br/> Fines paid in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=19'>Deu 22:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=29'>Deu 22:29</a><br/> Fees paid in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=8'>1Sa 9:8</a><br/> Sanctuary revenues paid in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=13'>Exo 30:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=32'>Neh 10:32</a><br/> Of different standards:<br/> - Of the sanctuary<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=13'>Exo 30:13</a> <br/> - Of the king's weight<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=26'>2Sa 14:26</a> <br/> Corrupted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=8&verse=5'>Amo 8:5</a>"}]}